## Envoy Gateway — API Gateway

Envoy Gateway là API gateway chính, cấu hình trong `infra/envoy-gateway/`:

```
envoy-gateway/
├── gatewayclass.yaml       # GatewayClass: envoy-gateway
├── gateway.yaml            # Gateway: puchi-gateway (HTTP, port 80)
├── envoyproxy.yaml         # EnvoyProxy: ClusterIP (ko expose LB)
├── puchi-api-service.yaml  # Service: puchi-api (ClusterIP:80)
├── reference-grant.yaml    # ReferenceGrant: cho phép cross-namespace
├── api-httproute.yaml      # HTTPRoute: route path prefix → backend services
└── api-securitypolicy.yaml # SecurityPolicy: CORS only (NO extAuth)
```

### HTTPRoute rules
| Path prefix | Backend | Namespace |
|-------------|---------|-----------|
| `/auth` | auth-service:8080 | puchi-backend |
| `/core` | core-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/content` | content-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/game` | game-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/grading` | grading-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/media` | media-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/notification` | notification-service:8000 | puchi-backend |
| `/user` | user-service:8000 | puchi-backend |

### SecurityPolicy (CORS only)
```yaml
cors:
  allowOrigins: ["https://puchi.io.vn", "http://localhost:3000"]
  allowCredentials: true
```
**Không có extAuth** — JWT verification do từng Go backend service tự xử lý qua `pkg/auth/`.

## Auth Flow (Infra layer)

```
Browser → Traefik/Cloudflare → Next.js PWA (puchi.io.vn)
                                    │
                                    ├─► api.puchi.io.vn/auth → auth-service:8080
                                    │     POST /login, POST /register, GET /social/...
                                    │
                                    └─► api.puchi.io.vn/{core,user,...} → Go services
                                          └── JWT verify local via JWKS (pkg/auth/)
```

**Auth-service không expose ra ngoài** — chỉ internal qua Envoy Gateway:
- Cluster DNS: `auth-service.puchi-backend.svc.cluster.local:8080`
- Public: `https://api.puchi.io.vn/auth/*`

## Frontend Deployment

File: `infra/frontend/web/deployment.yaml`

### Env vars
| Env | Value |
|-----|-------|
| NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL | `https://puchi.io.vn` |
| NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL | `https://api.puchi.io.vn` |
| NODE_ENV | production |

Namespace: `puchi-frontend` | Service: `web-service:3000` (ClusterIP)
